#: ../../../manual/3d_interaction/transform_control/pivot_point/3d_cursor.rst:66
msgid ""
"snaps the cursor to the currently selected vertex, edge or face. In Object "
"mode this option will snap the cursor to the center of the currently "
"selected Object."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/3d_interaction/transform_control/pivot_point/3d_cursor.rst:68
msgid "Cursor to Center"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/3d_interaction/transform_control/pivot_point/3d_cursor.rst:69
msgid "snaps the cursor to the origin point of the grid (location 0,0)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/3d_interaction/transform_control/pivot_point/3d_cursor.rst:70
msgid "Cursor to Grid"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/3d_interaction/transform_control/pivot_point/3d_cursor.rst:71
msgid "snaps the cursor to the nearest *visible* part of the grid."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/3d_interaction/transform_control/pivot_point/3d_cursor.rst:73
msgid "Cursor to Active"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/3d_interaction/transform_control/pivot_point/3d_cursor.rst:73
msgid ""
"snaps the cursor to the *active* (last selected) object, edge, face or "
"vertex."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/3d_interaction/transform_control/pivot_point/3d_cursor.rst:81
msgid ""
"**Center of the bounding box** surrounding the objects' centers in Object "
"mode or the **center of the bounding box** surrounding the selected vertices"
" when in *Edit* mode."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/3d_interaction/transform_control/pivot_point/3d_cursor.rst:84
msgid ""
"When the *Median Point* pivot point is selected, *Cursor to Selected* will "
"snap the 3D cursor to:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/3d_interaction/transform_control/pivot_point/3d_cursor.rst:87
msgid ""
"The median of the object centers in Object mode and the median of the "
"selected vertices in *Edit* mode."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/3d_interaction/transform_control/pivot_point/3d_cursor.rst:100
msgid ""
"The 3D cursor can also be positioned by entering Numeric location values "
"into the *3D cursor* panel of the *Properties* shelf (:kbd:`N`)."
msgstr ""

